<div class="greeting">Dear <%= candidateName %>,</div>

<div class="content">
    Welcome to <%= companyName %>! We're thrilled to have you register with our consultancy services.
</div>

<div class="content">
    Your profile has been successfully created in our system. Our team will review your details and reach out to you with relevant job opportunities that match your skills and experience.
</div>

<div class="info-box">
    <div class="info-box-title">Your Profile Summary</div>
    <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Name:</td>
            <td><%= candidateName %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Email:</td>
            <td><%= candidateEmail %></td>
        </tr>
        <% if (candidatePhone) { %>
        <tr>
            <td>Phone:</td>
            <td><%= candidatePhone %></td>
        </tr>
        <% } %>
        <% if (candidatePosition) { %>
        <tr>
            <td>Position:</td>
            <td><%= candidatePosition %></td>
        </tr>
        <% } %>
    </table>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <strong>Next Steps:</strong>
    <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
        <li>Our recruiters will review your profile within 2-3 business days</li>
        <li>We'll contact you when we find matching opportunities</li>
        <li>Keep your phone and email accessible for quick updates</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="button-container">
    <a href="<%= portalLink %>" class="cta-button">View Your Profile</a>
</div>

<div class="content" style="margin-top: 30px;">
    If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at any time.
</div>

<div class="content">
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The <%= companyName %> Team</strong>
</div>
